6
0:00:28.16,000 --> 0:00:31,000
using observational data.

7
0:00:31.16,000 --> 0:00:34,000
And I've been moonlighting for the last five years

8
0:00:34.16,000 --> 0:00:37,000
helping with a project in Africa.

9
0:00:37.16,000 --> 0:00:41,000
